{"prompt": "Create a professional website for a patent law firm. The design should be precise, using an Indian yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>InnoGuard Patent Law</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #e6b42e; /* Indian Yellow */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #b38e24 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        #main {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        #main h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #e6b42e; /* Indian Yellow */\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #eee;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #b38e24; /* Darker Indian Yellow */\n        }\n        .service-item p {\n            font-size: 14px;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #e6b42e; /* Indian Yellow */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n        .contact-form {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        .contact-form input[type=\"text\"],\n        .contact-form input[type=\"email\"],\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 80%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n        }\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: #b38e24; /* Darker Indian Yellow */\n            color: white;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #997a1f; /* Even darker Indian Yellow */\n        }\n        .grid-container {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>InnoGuard Patent Law</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center;\">InnoGuard Patent Law is a premier intellectual property law firm dedicated to safeguarding your innovations. We provide expert legal counsel and strategic guidance to secure and enforce patent rights for individuals, startups, and established corporations.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"services\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"grid-container\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Patent Prosecution</h3>\n                    <p>Drafting, filing, and prosecuting patent applications domestically and internationally.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Patentability Searches</h3>\n                    <p>Assessing the novelty and inventiveness of your ideas before filing.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Freedom-to-Operate Analysis</h3>\n                    <p>Identifying potential patent infringements for your products or processes.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Patent Litigation Support</h3>\n                    <p>Assisting in the enforcement and defense of patent rights.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>IP Strategy Consulting</h3>\n                    <p>Developing comprehensive strategies for your intellectual property portfolio.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Licensing & Agreements</h3>\n                    <p>Negotiating and drafting agreements for patent licensing and technology transfer.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center;\">Let us help you protect your groundbreaking ideas. Reach out to us for a consultation.</p>\n            <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required><br>\n                    <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required><br>\n                    <textarea name=\"message\" rows=\"5\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea><br>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 InnoGuard Patent Law. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}